	</figure>
      --><pb facs="page_image14"/><div><head>B<lb/>IS FOR<lb/>BILLY</head><lg><l>BILLY can never make up his<lb/>mind</l><l>Whether he wants to be</l><l>A Circus Clown in the sawdust<lb/>ring</l><l>Or a Pirate on the Sea!</l></lg><pb facs="page_image15"/>
